{"type": "article", "id": 50127, "title": "山东如意收购 Bally，以及，来看看纽约时装周 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-11T04:19:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2114, "name": "Bottega Veneta"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 47724, "name": "G-SHOCK"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 3112, "name": "Bally"}, {"id": 25622, "name": "山东如意"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180211115719wjJYnftS0Zk1XLlW.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/5a349e56-0da8-11e8-8eb7-42f857ea9f09\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>山东如意收购了 Bally</strong></a> | 山东如意集团近日宣布，从 JAB 集团手中收购了瑞士奢侈品牌 Bally 的控股权，具体交易价格未公开。 Bally 创立于 1851 年，在 1986 年进入中国市场，目前，中国市场的销售额占比超过了 50%，去年 Bally 邀请唐嫣担任亚太区品牌形象大使。上个月来自<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-01-08/china-s-ruyi-is-said-to-emerge-as-leading-bidder-for-bally\" rel=\"nofollow\">彭博社</a>的消息透露，山东如意集团以 7 亿美元的收购价格超过复星、七匹狼、赫美，成为 Bally 的领先竞购方。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/L-Oreal-ready-to-buy-shareholder-Nestle-s-stake-in-the-firm-says-CEO,946045.html#.Wn-qmJP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>欧莱雅打算回购雀巢持有的股份</strong></a> | 在周五的新闻发布会上，欧莱雅集团 CEO Jean-Paul Agon 表示，如果雀巢将出售其持有的欧莱雅 23% 的股份，欧莱雅随时准备回购，目前欧莱雅集团持有 18 亿欧元的现金，也考虑通过出售 Sanofi 的股份、向银行借贷来准备更充足的回购资金。前日，欧莱雅公布第四季度业绩显示，公司纯利润年增长 15.3%，至 35.8 亿欧元。雀巢自 1974 年以来一直是欧莱雅的主要投资者，去年欧莱雅的女继承人莉莉安·贝登古去世，雀巢与创始家族达成协议，规定双方在莉莉安·贝登古在世时以及去世后至少六个月不能增加化妆品集团的股份。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>为纪念即将离任的创意总监 Christopher Bailey 这十七年来的贡献，Burberry 在 Apple Music 上发表<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-09/17-years-of-soundtracks/topics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">《17 years of soundtracks》</a>，公开回顾 Burberry 在过去 17 年里的各种时装秀、全球营销活动及广告中所使用的歌曲。 </p><p>另外，Christopher Bailey 的告别作将于 2 月 17 日在伦敦举行，最后一场秀的配乐也会被加入到这张专辑里面。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114722KZximJ9fY32cNMHC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.686364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>3 月 2 日，<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-10/gshock-nagabayu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">G-SHOCK </a>将与近年来大热的日本创作者长场雄合作，发布手绘图案限定款手表。同时，还有与 BEAMS 合作的 T 恤、帽子等单品发售，这块特别版手表售价为 15000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114803vGJuQO3UsT6weHR4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114808uG3jIMFgNS4mHsLi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.754545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114803isHawt60fVkB9NQv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114816xHL5A7ngmFh1CSdk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114816q9QHPrpzm6oxie0X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114803dMyXkNGopIlBCSu0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>纽约时装周的天猫中国日，陈冠希带着 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/clot-fallwinter-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CLOT </a>登场了。</p><p>此次正好是 CLOT 品牌创立 15 周年，以“过去、现在、未来”为主题，CLOT 延续街头文化 Converse、Herschel、Dr.Woo、sacai、Fear of God、SOME WARE 等品牌的合作款。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114851ehWRCnAj8Bi6LaDb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114842s0v7wVEf2orSi19Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114842wmGXpejHEah6kC8J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114843K7efdSXI2Pu1tk06.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111148436MNOVuXBsPIqdJ1Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021111484531moxkZWjOhiKzQR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114844W6LIbMzVNJ2w0GmO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111148450tKneEy1jZ7xNkzR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114846CkVlJsNzB6dRHtPD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114846y1rc5Rg9nx3p6mEo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114851whisxjLo2IlBgdMS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111148524A5stY9ENMqglyQv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111148527Hs5eob1gNlKyzQU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114859DAIxR4Q3ysuBN7E9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114859ZShm6yPX85EHdu49.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114859ibsud6fpNkyMFD9r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114913ktluvcSME4s7yzLD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/article/metro-boomin-tom-ford-nyfw-diary-fall-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tom Ford </a>在纽约时装周上分别发布了男装和女装系列。</p><p>Tom Ford 想用皮草、豹纹、蛇纹和亮色西装讲述复古狂野的故事，但可惜的是，这些元素除了制造简单的视觉冲击，本身并没有太多的亮点可讲。 </p><p>《纽约时报》说，“Tom Ford 丢掉了他的酷”。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115011T1ZuApKYs5q0kc8y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115013ZK2eHufIGqr34vxV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115013IbaBQuykZ1iYl02T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115019tPQyZehX4SW1f0is.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115019UKT2NgDPfCWBLcMZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115041xn9ahQcUljZkgvCi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115042PNCgeHQs4V3R8jWF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115042S5AKm1G46qQ3HIwJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115043ChUDmsBwgfMEec9K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115057gtaC3OwsqIvG9DFZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115058OYi0Mvrm9jUL8tGg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115111YA58wuzRDNvV7o4L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018021111511310sJb2OPKU9tYNpq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115114ysRE0hpiIcjGTBeY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115115C6WVbH2zL48rdgjw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115115mBqFx8wz6OVModb1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115115qAG5upToicYy3ab6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500274\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>这一季的 <a href=\"https://www.wallpaper.com/fashion/fashionweeks/womenswear-aw-2018/new-york/bottega-veneta-aw-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bottega Veneta</a> 只在纽约时装周走秀。为了庆祝麦迪逊大街全新开幕的旗舰店，Bottega Veneta 以探索纽约都市生活为主题，打造了男女款丝制睡衣、轻柔的晚礼服。 </p><p>值得一说的是，此前 Bottega Veneta 宣布从米兰时装周搬到纽约，是为了打破品牌过于内敛、沉闷的困境，获取年轻人的注意力，这次的大秀上，Bottega 让 Gigi Hadid 压轴出场似乎也是看中了她在年轻消费者中的影响力。不过，但从这一季的产品本身来看，Bottega 想赢得年轻人的欢心，可能还是有点困难。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115147INuxiz8HevFb9GoD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115148GQb5YMlI9ZKoD7mp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115159gWXSPZep5HvGYauQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115212hzCgDjcSrJoyMwin.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115212RfvBwzULH5Gm8pOJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115217fYxekZzTgPOVwmc8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115432Qezh6kiqYwKFrWnP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115433MpCwo12zkciqY4xU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115434gJKySCofBI15nFpT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115435AvdNQKGp2WIyYOMh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115435s1iV4m3cRI59UQAq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111154359PtxqMpUeLbcTVHD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115436uwfCD0JHaIV1Yiz9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115437IoGZ2enwDi7yNsYa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111154379mfu52hTeiYMj1G7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115437U39J4wtaslq8Djbd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115438PEyQs6zGlRJZj205.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115438CvRJ7WSmTutFQ3ZG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115440PBOgzNbpSvLTdRIY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115440DpFtSRWJPGdn48AQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115441Gdn3M4SXBxaAy21Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115441uC96GdPHKlLsJvEI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115441ztlourkh1A6Usq3C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Bottega Veneta</p>"}